@skills/backend.md

You are working on a GO module's API app. Use Fastify via `@tmlmobilidade/fastify`, Zod schemas from `@tmlmobilidade/types`, MongoDB via `@tmlmobilidade/interfaces` and `@tmlmobilidade/mongo`. Controllers must be static classes. Routes register in `endpoints/[resource]/[resource].routes.ts`, handlers in `[resource].controller.ts`. Always use the standard response helpers and error codes defined in the skill above.
